e websites may also be subject to other agreements and information provided in these websites. 2. Product Information&lt;/h3>\\r\\n&lt;ul>\\r\\n&lt;li>Nothing on these websites should be considered a solicitation to buy or an offer to sell a security or any other investment product or service, by any person in any jurisdiction or country where such offer, solicitation, purchase, sale, or other product or service would be contrary to any applicable local law or regulation or would subject T. Rowe Price to any registration or licensing requirement in such jurisdiction. It is your responsibility to inform yourself of any applicable legal and regulatory restrictions and to ensure that your access and use of this information does not contravene any such restrictions and to observe all applicable laws and regulations of any relevant jurisdiction. Professional advice should be sought in cases of doubt, as any failure to do so may constitute a breach of the securities laws in any such jurisdiction.&lt;br>\\r\\n&lt;br>\\r\\n&lt;/li>\\r\\n&lt;li>Each time you access these websites for any purpose, you shall be deemed to represent, warrant and covenant to T. Rowe Price that you are not (a) located in, or a national or resident of, or associated with the government of, any country that is subject to trade sanctions, or (b) on any prohibited party list or acting on behalf of or owned or controlled by any person or entity on any such list.&lt;/li>\\r\\n&lt;/ul>\\r\\n&#34;}}\" id=\"product-information\" class=\"cmp-text\"> 2. Product Information Nothing on these websites should be considered a solicitation to buy or an offer to sell a security or any other investment product or service, by any person in any jurisdiction or country where such offer, solicitation, purchase, sale, or other product or service would be contrary to any applicable local law or regulation or would subject T. Rowe Price to any registration or licensing requirement in such jurisdiction. It is your responsibility to inform yourself of any applicable legal and regulatory restrictions and to ensure that your access and use of this information does not contravene any such restrictions and to observe all applicable laws and regulations of any relevant jurisdiction. Professional advice should be sought in cases of doubt, as any failure to do so may constitute a breach of the securities laws in any such jurisdiction. Each time you access these websites for any purpose, you shall be deemed to represent, warrant and covenant to T. Rowe Price that you are not (a) located in, or a national or resident of, or associated with the government of, any country that is subject to trade sanctions, or (b) on any prohibited party list or acting on behalf of or owned or controlled by any person or entity on any such list. 3. Limitations Regarding Information Presented&lt;/h3>\\r\\n&lt;ul>\\r\\n&lt;li>These websites are not intended to provide legal, tax, or investment advice. In general, the information contained in these websites has been prepared without reference to any particular user’s personal situation. Unless specifically stated otherwise, these websites do not provide recommendations concerning investments, investment strategies, or account types; they are not individualized to the needs of any specific investor and are not intended to suggest that any particular investment action is appropriate for you., Any tax-related discussion contained in these websites, including any attachments/links, is not intended or written to be used, and cannot be used, for the purpose of (i) avoiding any tax penalties or (ii) promoting, marketing, or recommending to any other party any transaction or matter addressed herein. Please consult your independent legal counsel and/or tax professional regarding any legal or tax issues raised in this material.&lt;br>\\r\\n&lt;br>\\r\\n&lt;/li>\\r\\n&lt;li>Before investing, you should consider whether any investment, investment strategy, security, other asset, or related transaction is appropriate for you based on your personal investment objectives, financial circumstances, and risk tolerance. You are also encouraged to consult your independent legal, tax, or investment professional regarding your specific situation.&lt;br>\\r\\n&lt;/li>\\r\\n&lt;/ul>\\r\\n&#34;}}\" id=\"information-presented\" class=\"cmp-text\"> 3. Limitations Regarding Information Presented These websites are not intended to provide legal, tax, or investment advice. In general, the information contained in these websites has been prepared without reference to any particular user’s personal situation. Unless specifically stated otherwise, these websites do not provide recommendations concerning investments, investment strategies, or account types; they are not individualized to the needs of any specific investor and are not intended to suggest that any particular investment action is appropriate for you., Any tax-related discussion contained in these websites, including any attachments/links, is not intended or written to be used, and cannot be used, for the purpose of (i) avoiding any tax penalties or (ii) promoting, marketing, or recommending to any other party any transaction or matter addressed herein. Please consult your independent legal counsel and/or tax professional regarding any legal or tax issues raised in this material. Before investing, you should consider whether any investment, investment strategy, security, other asset, or related transaction is appropriate for you based on your personal investment objectives, financial circumstances, and risk tolerance. You are also encouraged to consult your independent legal, tax, or investment professional regarding your specific situation. 4. Privacy of Information&lt;/h3>\\r\\n&lt;ul>\\r\\n&lt;li>While using these websites, you may be asked to provide certain information to us, such as categories of products and services in which you are interested, account information, or contact or other personal information, in order to use certain capabilities and/or to invest in T. Rowe Price products or enroll in T. Rowe Price services.&lt;/li>\\r\\n&lt;/ul>\\r\\n&lt;ul>\\r\\n&lt;li>All such information may be accessible to T. Rowe Price personnel, is subject to possible retention, and may be used and disclosed consistent with our Privacy Notice, which can be accessed at any time by clicking on the Privacy Notice link that is in the footer of each page of these websites.&lt;/li>\\r\\n&lt;/ul>\\r\\n&lt;ul>\\r\\n&lt;/ul>\\r\\n&#34;}}\" id=\"privacy-information\" class=\"cmp-text\"> 4. Privacy of Information While using these websites, you may be asked to provide certain information to us, such as categories of products and services in which you are interested, account information, or contact or other personal information, in order to use certain capabilities and/or to invest in T. Rowe Price products or enroll in T. Rowe Price services. All such information may be accessible to T. Rowe Price personnel, is subject to possible retention, and may be used and disclosed consistent with our Privacy Notice, which can be accessed at any time by clicking on the Privacy Notice link that is in the footer of each page of these websites. 5. Intellectual Property Rights&lt;/h3>\\r\\n&lt;ul>\\r\\n&lt;li>&lt;b>Ownership:&lt;/b> These websites, including the content made available on or generated through use of these websites, including, but not limited to any and all text, graphics, layout, software code, applications, data, information, displays, images, audio, video, designs, domain names, trademarks, trade names and trade identities, materials, the look and feel of these websites, the compilation, assembly and arrangement of the content of these websites; and downloadable and non-downloadable output generated through your use of these websites (Site Content) are owned, controlled or licensed by T. Rowe Price, its subsidiaries, or its affiliates, and are protected from unauthorized